		<h2 class="font__headline">Guidelines</h2>

		<h3 class="font__title">Font Face</h3>
		<p><strong>Roboto</strong> is the <em>only</em> font family that should be used. Any exceptions require UX approval.</p>

		<h3 class="font__title">Font Styles</h3>
		<p>Font styles should only be selected from the UX approved list of predefined styles, outlined on this page. <em>In other words, do not write application-specific CSS for typography styles.</em> Instead, use the provided classes and helpers. Any exceptions require UX approval.</p>
		<p>Follow any listed use case guidelines when applying typography styles.</p>

		<h3 class="font__title">Text Colors</h3>
		<p>Text colors are part of the <a ui-sref="colors">Colors component</a>.</p>

		<h3 class="font__title">Line Length / Readability</h3>
		<p>For best readability, lines of text should be no longer than ~60 characters. Shorter lines of text should wrap at ~30 characters or less.</p>

		<h3 class="font__title">Additional Guidelines</h3>
		<p><a href="https://material.io/guidelines/style/typography.html" title="Typography specs for Material Design"><abbr title="Material Design">MD</abbr> typography specs</a> are an extension of DS UI, and should be referred to for further guidance.</p>
	</div>

